      "id": "wb-intro-text",
      "type": "text",
      "props": {
        "text": "<h2>Not another flat website builder. A launch system.</h2><p>Your website should not sit there looking pretty while leads leak away. The Gr8 Result AI Website Builder connects design, SEO copy, service pages, forms, bookings, CRM, email marketing, SMS marketing and automation into one build flow.</p><p>Use AI to create the first version, choose the industry direction, then refine every section with visual controls. The result is a fast, mobile-friendly, no-code business website that looks sharp, explains the offer clearly, ranks for relevant search terms, captures leads properly and plugs directly into the rest of your business system.</p>",
        "alignment": "center",
        "minHeight": "360px",
        "textColor": "#e5f7ff",
        "textFontSize": 21,
        "textLineHeight": 1.55,
        "backgroundColor": "#101926",
